description:
Merchants that operate dance studios, dance schools, and public
dance halls or ballrooms, and charge for admission fees, lessons, and
refreshments. Such merchants may teach many types of dance or
specialize in tap and ballet, ballroom, square dance instruction, or
other types of dance.
